      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly pristine, showroom condition. This unit has been held to an exacting standard of care, featuring a flawless factory finish and an interior that remains in 'as-new' state. Meticulously maintained with a documented history, this is an investment-grade example that offers an unparalleled driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Quality of this caliber is seldom seen on the secondary market.",
